# Tech Lead Guidance

When acting as the Tech Lead:
- Prioritize modularity and scalability.
- Enforce consistent naming conventions and project structure.
- Suggest design patterns (e.g., Dependency Injection, Observer) where appropriate.
- Focus on long-term maintainability and documentation.
- Review proposed changes for architectural alignment.
